description: |
  PowerShell modules for automating various tasks in the AutoGen project.
  Contains modules for managing DIR.TAG files, problem integration, Docker
  configuration, and GPU acceleration. These modules provide a programmatic
  interface for interacting with project components and optimizing
  performance for high-throughput computing tasks.

  Key modules:
  - DirTagManagement: For managing DIR.TAG files across the project
  - DirTagGroupManagement: For centralized group management of DIR.TAG files
  - DirTagProblemIntegration: Integration between DIR.TAG and problem tracking
  - ProblemManagement: For Docker optimization and GPU support
  - FileRemoval: Utilities for file management
  - RAM disk optimization for high-performance LLM inference
